category: ORGAN RECITAL
category comment: 

clue: This organ breaks down ingested nutrients into small particles & mixes them with gastric juices to make chyme

response: the stomach

clue: The trigone is a triangular area of this organ between the opening of the urethra & the 2 ureters

response: the bladder

clue: The diencephalon, part of this organ, includes the thalamus

response: the brain

clue: The epicardium is its outer layer

response: the heart

clue: Each of these organs has a visceral pleura & a parietal pleura

response: the lungs

